WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.780
I found a good place to take Dad.

00:03.340 --> 00:07.550
It’s not far from home, and there aren’t many people around there.

00:07.550 --> 00:09.960
I’ll take Dad there tomorrow.

00:10.560 --> 00:13.700
If I take everything, though, it will be very heavy.

00:13.700 --> 00:14.950
How will I do it?

00:15.570 --> 00:18.300
If I carry something that large, someone is bound to notice.

00:18.680 --> 00:20.750
How about the electricity and the cords?

00:21.520 --> 00:22.350
Impossível, ele disse.

00:22.350 --> 00:25.310
I’ll need help.
